{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>social deduction roguelike</strong> where your <strong>deck is full of lies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your deck was infiltrated by Demons. They will bluff, lie and manipulate to stay hidden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal? Find and Kill all of them before its too late. But be careful, one wrong execution and the entire town will suffer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522600/extras/killingevil.gif?t=1740676275\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUILD A DECK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each run, <strong>build and refine your deck</strong> of villagers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the end of each day, remove weak villagers, recruit stronger ones, or upgrade those you trust. But beware, new arrivals may not be who they seem. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522600/extras/revealcards.gif?t=1740676275\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SOCIAL DEDUCTION AND ROGUELIKE?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each day, <strong>demons grow stronger</strong>, gaining new abilities and even summoning Minions to deceive you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you make too many mistakes and kill innocents - your run is over, but each failure will bring new insights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522600/extras/eyelooking2.gif?t=1740676275\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNIQUE CHARACTERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are <strong>4 types of characters,\u00a0</strong>each with unique abilities that alter the game in different ways.\u00a0They will all find their way into your deck.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Villagers</strong>\u00a0- Help uncover demons, protect the town or provide other special benefits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Outcasts</strong>\u00a0- Have harmful abilities, but are still Good. So don't kill them, learn to work around their flaws.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Minions</strong> - Loyal to the demons, they spread lies and deceive you. Find and execute them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Demons</strong>\u00a0- Masters of deception. They will bluff, manipulate and mislead to stay hidden.\u00a0Find and execute them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522600/extras/cardreveal2.gif?t=1740676275\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3522600?t=1740676275","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3522600?t=1740676275","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522600/15acd86605e430f81b3bf14c9a1f3cbd3bb6e614/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740676275","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3522600/15acd86605e430f81b3bf14c9a1f3cbd3bb6e614/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740676275","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>social deduction roguelike</strong> where your <strong>deck is full of lies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your deck was infiltrated by Demons. They will bluff, lie and manipulate to stay hidden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal? Find and Kill all of them before its too late. But be careful, one wrong execution and the entire town will suffer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com